    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/e0e300a4a593a88af69c1b67ad52a8b0.avif?t=1766077797\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/585e37e3552370281228ed2cf12135e9.poster.avif?t=1766077797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/585e37e3552370281228ed2cf12135e9.webm?t=1766077797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/585e37e3552370281228ed2cf12135e9.mp4?t=1766077797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好在《有缘千里来相创》的世界中开始乱斗吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/1983f323e52d3db8d9f894028fe8ffb2.avif?t=1766077797\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/01699ed228486662067490f428275d5a.poster.avif?t=1766077797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/01699ed228486662067490f428275d5a.webm?t=1766077797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/01699ed228486662067490f428275d5a.mp4?t=1766077797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过本地或线上模式与朋友较量，让他们看看在这款高速激烈战斗的游戏中，谁才是王者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向对手蹦跶、将他们丢到墙上来让场地旋转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用凝滞来防御危险的攻击，找寻合适的机会将对手丢进虚无，可别错过这场精彩的乱斗咯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/6a40291d45830b85300078b4307cb84c.avif?t=1766077797\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/901b5f69b0abc1b3d6482015e8e7d078.poster.avif?t=1766077797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/901b5f69b0abc1b3d6482015e8e7d078.webm?t=1766077797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/901b5f69b0abc1b3d6482015e8e7d078.mp4?t=1766077797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*竞技场（线上模式）将逐步推出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108230/extras/b060f47525983fff5507e75d67ea6290.avif?t=1766077797\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乱斗时间到：想要获胜，就把对手丢出屏幕外吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 两键乱斗类游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 有回合数和生命数的经典1v1对战模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 沙发合作多人游玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 线上多人游玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以拿起手柄，下定决心，在《有缘千里来相创》中进行无与伦比的对决吧！</p>",
